{"tid":46381,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[初嘗遊記] 5日4夜 台中 花蓮 孝子團","createTime":"2016-12-19T15:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T12:01:13.000Z","uid":3932,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"742f2f804e0f41853b1d05b7753e7355de7bd580","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:16:57.000Z","msg":"好喇，各位入嚟之前，可能會奇怪：點解係台中＋花蓮一東一西咁奇怪？<br />\n<br />\n事情是咁的，當時hkexpress開花蓮新航線，有＄68機票。中學嗰陣跟學校去過一次花蓮，有幾個景點都覺得幾靚，於是乎作為孝子嘅我，即刻狗衡買咗話帶媽咪去。<br />\n<br />\n原定12月6日出發，玩到11號。但最終因為有科要做test，撞咗時間。唯有重新買過<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 申請咗退稅但未回音，有冇巴絲知會搞幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼續。<br />\n<br />\n夾過晒價之後，最終買咗12月19－23號台中機票。但真係好想去花蓮，所以就決定台中＋花蓮<br />\n<br />\n下篇會講正文。"},{"pid":"1872c535a059de9f4afc2a39360eac35609d002d","tid":46381,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7d7564eb06a978bafab74a53db8ece17c867d12a","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"正文<br />\n<br />\n9點半機，6點半出門搭巴士，因為我凌晨3點先收工，完全冇瞓過。<br />\n<br />\n上到車立即柒瞓，到大嶼山就醒咗，朝早嘅天氣真係幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9MP32xm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MP32xm.jpg&h=4bff0f4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"365eefc580474c468265182e07dc197a834fc51b","tid":46381,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"我想知台中點去花蓮 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5318f8464b865e38923d63eed6f152ba6f9198e2","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"上到機唔知點解唔眼瞓......癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是開始畫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6afx94f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6afx94f.jpg&h=a7fe534f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">有興趣可以follow我ig: wyc_sketcher</span></span><br />\n<br />\n落機atm提款，撳咗好少，12000NT，預自己冇嘢好買<br />\n<br />\n之後指定動作去中華電信COUNTER 買PREPAID CARD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/233504_541b907b446fa665d79971a7300f9129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F233504_541b907b446fa665d79971a7300f9129.jpg&h=4885ec67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無限data，speedtest 過都有9.3Mbps，睇youtube都ok"},{"pid":"d53be4e7d0f10ba63ad41d423726d2d3d48e382e","tid":46381,"uid":42569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"Live"},{"pid":"4738e520773d231a942a7213c2e4e3ac6b0d6e20","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"有巴打問我點樣台中去花蓮<br />\n<br />\n用極on9方法：<br />\n<br />\n13：39 台中高鐵－＞14：28 台北高鐵<br />\n再轉<br />\n15：53 台北台鐵－＞18：58 花蓮台鐵<br />\n<br />\n搭的士去高鐵站果陣，司機大哥話其實我地可以包車行中間d山路，因為風景好靚，又唔洗兜大圈轉黎轉去<br />\n<br />\n我知錯啦媽咪，下次唔會咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a15fa71bed1aa851c0efb715106a4df1cdb945","tid":46381,"uid":63188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"認真，台中的士佬好好人，好熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536c799ed85fddb86fdef18256c2d9138862c88d","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，台中的士佬好好人，好熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真👍"},{"pid":"d6744de8c290533e61c528db73a61ce4bb3f75eb","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"頂唔住 瞓先"},{"pid":"4de3df71f6162471b5a10714e157201e92fb2902","tid":46381,"uid":28588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"中間座山會經過清境 武嶺 合歡山 太魯閣 好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc 但會坐到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"1312d1e18f7bac7cb50b2556e7ee314c98dc228c","tid":46381,"uid":14539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T20:57:06.000Z","msg":"台中唔係可以搭個架自強號去花蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月尾都係要台中去花蓮 求解答"},{"pid":"a0514a2662c611689f296c65841c27ecae35c9f8","tid":46381,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T21:16:56.000Z","msg":"畫幾靚<br />\n快d更新"},{"pid":"9852dfbf6ff840c9aafaf529ba0072f4c893a22a","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台中唔係可以搭個架自強號去花蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月尾都係要台中去花蓮 求解答</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接搭自強會有排坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我先搭高鐵去台北 再轉台鐵去花蓮"},{"pid":"8db87ac92b029d9317da740ebd2163cd95d37e68","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:42:51.000Z","msg":"下晝一點幾，台中高鐵站<br />\n台妹走光了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLaaTQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLaaTQn.jpg&h=d31d19f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一時間去便利店買純喫茶 真係好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/074223_be34204d15b967958ff85820ce5516ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F074223_be34204d15b967958ff85820ce5516ba.jpg&h=dc1775ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐得幾舒服，一個鐘唔洗就到台北"},{"pid":"263401f8c775351436d1603486d849eecfc297e7","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"食緊早餐 天氣好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2116bS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2116bS.jpg&h=0bac8019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a25bdf0e33ce4569668bf3c1bc691d62d3b0a013","tid":46381,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有巴打問我點樣台中去花蓮<br />\n<br />\n用極on9方法：<br />\n<br />\n13：39 台中高鐵－＞14：28 台北高鐵<br />\n再轉<br />\n15：53 台北台鐵－＞18：58 花蓮台鐵<br />\n<br />\n搭的士去高鐵站果陣，司機大哥話其實我地可以包車行中間d山路，因為風景好靚，又唔洗兜大圈轉黎轉去<br />\n<br />\n我知錯啦媽咪，下次唔會咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶住媽咪<br />\n搭火車去花蓮其實OK<br />\n<br />\n包車台中去花蓮除咗貴，時間唔會慳好多<br />\n唯一風景係靚<br />\n條公路依山而建又多彎<br />\n唔搭得車隨時勁暈車浪<br />\n<br />\n利申: 月頭先帶過屋企人遊花蓮"},{"pid":"0434f885926201112f9aedf2ebfbf5c77776e639","tid":46381,"uid":14539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台中唔係可以搭個架自強號去花蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月尾都係要台中去花蓮 求解答</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接搭自強會有排坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我先搭高鐵去台北 再轉台鐵去花蓮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見自強都係4個鐘內"},{"pid":"69a3dbc19e3dcadfb3892035c122516e23af7795","tid":46381,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台中唔係可以搭個架自強號去花蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月尾都係要台中去花蓮 求解答</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接搭自強會有排坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我先搭高鐵去台北 再轉台鐵去花蓮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見自強都係4個鐘內</blockquote><br />\n揀&quot;太魯閣&quot;或者&quot;普悠瑪&quot;的自強號班次<br />\n快一般自強號好多<br />\n<br />\n不過要早兩個星期上網搶飛"},{"pid":"b58ba099dddc95298d114ca49e6309944f6e6a63","tid":46381,"uid":17611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上到機唔知點解唔眼瞓......癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是開始畫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6afx94f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6afx94f.jpg&h=a7fe534f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">有興趣可以follow我ig: wyc_sketcher</span></span><br />\n<br />\n落機atm提款，撳咗好少，12000NT，預自己冇嘢好買<br />\n<br />\n之後指定動作去中華電信COUNTER 買PREPAID CARD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/233504_541b907b446fa665d79971a7300f9129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F233504_541b907b446fa665d79971a7300f9129.jpg&h=4885ec67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無限data，speedtest 過都有9.3Mbps，睇youtube都ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打用咩筆畫？"},{"pid":"0a3207290b78d4288561c44caf86414e74c04edd","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打用咩筆畫？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n櫻花嗰隻針筆 0.1mm"},{"pid":"82ec4d1293f2b3c1f404bd1b1b8b4106c7d1ba42","tid":46381,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"今日包車遊太魯閣 司機應該都幾後生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/151657_3176c97bf34666d9b8542e02ce828198.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F151657_3176c97bf34666d9b8542e02ce828198.jpg&h=b41f24bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一站 七星潭<br />\n中學嗰陣跟學校團嚟過 比記憶中更加靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<